WEBVTT

00:02.154 --> 00:03.833
I came as soon as I got the call.

00:03.868 --> 00:04.862
What's going on?

00:04.896 --> 00:06.297
Sorry to pull you in this late.

00:06.331 --> 00:07.631
We just tracked down our perp.

00:07.666 --> 00:10.148
Lieutenant, this is
the doctor I mentioned.

00:10.252 --> 00:11.747
Yes. Forensic psychologist?

00:11.812 --> 00:12.870
That's right.

00:12.904 --> 00:14.071
Nice to meet you.

00:14.105 --> 00:15.306
Where's Crane?

00:15.340 --> 00:18.309
He's already interrogating
the suspect.

00:18.343 --> 00:20.811
What do you mean,
Crane's interrogating the suspect?

00:21.288 --> 00:23.812
We know you saw more
than you admitted.

00:24.182 --> 00:26.550
Tell us.
We mean you no harm.

00:26.585 --> 00:29.853
The suspect is obviously
teeing up an insanity defense.

00:29.888 --> 00:31.188
She's smart.

00:31.222 --> 00:33.324
She knows exactly what she's doing.

00:33.358 --> 00:34.858
She?

00:34.893 --> 00:37.027
Why is that?

00:37.062 --> 00:40.297
Why are you deceiving us?

00:40.332 --> 00:42.199
What did you see?

00:43.668 --> 00:45.436
Abbie!

00:46.404 --> 00:48.472
What is going on here?

00:48.506 --> 00:51.976
We finally caught Abigail Mills.
Mostly thanks to the good doctor here.

00:52.010 --> 00:56.246
Caught? I don't understand.
She didn't do anything wrong.

00:56.281 --> 00:57.281
Did she?

00:57.315 --> 00:59.850
I think you know
the answer to that.

01:04.289 --> 01:05.822
Stop lying, Abbie.

01:06.925 --> 01:09.293
The truth will set you free.

01:13.732 --> 01:15.532
Captain!

01:16.434 --> 01:18.248
The door's locked!

01:18.504 --> 01:20.222
Sir!

01:21.039 --> 01:23.207
Let me out of here!

01:23.241 --> 01:25.242
Someone let me out of here!

01:29.948 --> 01:32.549
Let me out! Let me out!

01:32.584 --> 01:33.748
Let me out!

01:33.820 --> 01:35.834
Let me out of here!

